data.title: Basic Crunch
instruction: Lie on your back with knees bent and feet flat on the ground
Place your hands streteched over your head
Lift your head, neck, and shoulders off the ground
Lower back down slowly and repeat

data.title: Plank
instruction: Start in a push-up position with your elbows bent and forearms on the ground
Keep your body in a straight line from head to heels
Hold the position while engaging your core
Avoid letting your hips sag or rise too high
